reviews.review_text: great sound, great setlist...... who wouldn't want a show like this? Definitely worthy of 4 stars. Don't care to much for that funky accordion though!?! Jerry's solos sweep the air beautifully to compensate.........Oh well I liked it , to each his/her own.
